{"_id":"870fd18e-7bdb-4703-90fa-c4607f013ffa","type":"ability","name":"Danger Sense","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/investigation.svg","system":{"skill":"Investigation","name":"Danger Sense","rank":"5","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"1","description":"Whenever you would be taken by surprise by an attack, trap, ambush, or other unexpected event, you may use this to immediately take a medium or fast action. This can be used to move out of range of traps, dangerous situations, or attacks.","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"investigation"}}
{"_id":"adafdcc5-bdea-4461-ab03-123a948c956f","type":"ability","name":"Quick Assessment","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/investigation.svg","system":{"skill":"Investigation","name":"Quick Assessment","rank":"1","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"intuition","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"1","description":"You spend 1 minute talking to someone. On a success, you gain enough understanding of them to know the best way to convince them to take a certain course of action (appeal to their morals, threaten them, bribe them, etc.). On a failure, add a Consequence to the tracker.","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"investigation"}}
{"_id":"bd6bf9b7-1184-4eba-ac1b-4a4c9af879df","type":"ability","name":"Line of Questioning","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/investigation.svg","system":{"skill":"Investigation","name":"Line of Questioning","rank":"1","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"intelligence","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"1","description":"You set up a clever line of questioning to back someone into a trap. After one minute of questioning, the target must either reveal a piece of information they wanted to keep hidden or take one intuition burn. On a failure, add a Consequence to the tracker.","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"investigation"}}
{"_id":"caeec7e9-74d8-44ee-9484-27f2ccb860ee","type":"ability","name":"Surveil","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/investigation.svg","system":{"skill":"Investigation","name":"Surveil","rank":"1","type":"activity","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"1","description":"You surveil a person or location for about an hour. You gain Suverillance Points equal to your investigation ranks. When interacting with that person or location in your current Venture, you may replace the results of any failed roll with an investigation check by spending one point. Alternatively, you can spend a point to remove one Consequence from the tracker.","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"investigation"}}
{"_id":"f80e52f8-4da7-4fef-99ec-e2258b380a2b","type":"ability","name":"Invasive Research","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/investigation.svg","system":{"skill":"Investigation","name":"Invasive Research","rank":"3","type":"activity","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"2","description":"You can research a person, talking to people who know them, searching public records, and so on. All social interactions you make with them gain a boon for the duration of this escapade.","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"investigation"}}
